    W(nn)     Perform "Wordflow":  i.e. assemble lines of text, placing
 or WW  WW    as many words as possible per line and doing left and
 or W    W    right justification.  A blank intermediate line can be used
 or WWWWWW    to create 'paragraphs'.
 
              EXAMPLE:  ???ww??????????????????????????????ww?????????????
                        *  A big fat cow was eating all the    Text
                        *    green grass, while   the sun      outside of
                        *    was shining. So too were the      the column
                        *    birds.                            will not
                        *                                      be
                        *  But a lion was watching             altered
                        *  this cow.                           at all.
 
              yields:
                        *  A big  fat cow was eating  all the  Text
                        *  green  grass,  while the  sun  was  outside of
                        *  shining.  So too were the birds.    the column
                        *                                      will not
                        *                                      be
                        *  But a lion was watching this cow.   altered
